                    <msContents>
                        <summary>The first volume of a Persian translation and commentary on the
                                <title>Qur‘ān</title>by <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc"
                                type="standard" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/20030140" key="n85026579"
                                >Kāshifī, Ḥusayn Vāʻiẓ, d. 1504 or 5</persName>. According to the
                            introduction the author had been engaged in composing a 4 volume
                            elaborated commentary called <title xml:lang="ara-latn-x-Lc">Javāhir
                                al-tafsīr</title><title xml:lang="ara">جواهر التفسیر</title> for
                                <name key="n85019117" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/22198747/"><persName
                                    xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" type="standard">Alisher Navoiĭ,
                                    1441-1501</persName><persName xml:lang="per">امیر علی
                                    شیر</persName></name>, when he interrupted his work after
                            completing the first volume in <date calendar="Gregorian" when="1492"
                                >897</date> to quickly prepare a simple translation entitled <title
                                xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc">Mavāhib-i ʻalīyah</title>
                            <title xml:lang="per">مواهب علية</title>. It was completed in two years
                            between <date calendar="Gregorian" from="1492" to="1494">897 and
                                899</date>. </summary>
                        <!-- summary description -->
                        <msItem>
                            <author ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/20030140" key="n85026579">
                                <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" type="standard">Kāshifī, Ḥusayn
                                    Vāʻiẓ, d. 1504 or 5</persName>
                                <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" type="alt">Ḥusain ibn ʻAlī Vāʻiẓ
                                    Kashifī, d. 910/1504</persName>
                                <persName xml:lang="per" type="alt">حسين بن علی واعظ
                                    کاشفى</persName>
                                <persName xml:lang="per">كاشفى، حسين واعض<surname/>
                                    <forename/>
                                    <addName xml:lang="ara" type="laqab"/>
                                    <addName xml:lang="ara" type="kunyah"/>
                                    <addName xml:lang="ara" type="khitab"/>
